SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 237, Northwest Territories
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 237 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES with respect to the spring flooding that occurred in the from May 7 to June 6, 2021.
